_sText: This is a new game type for css. Yes, I do appreciate everybody for telling me what to fix on this map. but sadly, this map isn't as good as it could be. This map is what I would like to call a "prototype map". I wasn't going to spend a lot of time on a experimental map if nobody was going to like it. So based on results of this "Prototype Map" I'll start making that insane basketball map soon. The map is an NBA style basketball court. Lots of custom textures, sorry for the map size. -Play to 30 -5 vs. 5 -Winner gets the choice of M3, Awp, or Para. -Loser dies THANKS TO JETLIP FOR THE BASIC SCORING SYSTEM Scoring System Shooting Tutorial
